data.description: Back on market!  Now nearly 10k under recent appraisal and brand new roof!  Beautiful 5 bed 3 full bath home in gorgeous Campbell Hills.  This clean and well maintained home has an updated kitchen and bathrooms, dining room, new light fixtures inside and out (2021), new garage doors (2021) and is completely move in ready. The main level features large living room with gas fireplace, laundry room, balcony, and primary bedroom with beautifully updated bathroom. Lower level could easily be used as an in-law suite with family room (second gas log fireplace), patio access, two additional bedrooms, full bath, and kitchenette in oversized garage. Enjoy the quiet neighborhood with park like, peaceful backyard. Wonderful schools and excellent location with a short commute to Roanoke or Blacksburg.
